  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is presented in the style of old 1st-person point & click adventure games, with an emphasis on moody atmosphere and surreal environments. Strange denizens pepper the vast halls of this cryptic building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957880/extras/ede73aba2dc0f4af181f9418115a9aab.avif?t=1753381252\" width=366 height=194 /></span>Learn the mysteries of the various rooms and complete a handful of puzzle minigames to reach the \"true end\". Or just have a relaxed time exploring and meeting folks, because most of the station is accessible from when you first enter the building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will one of these fine folk become your artistic muse!?!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957880/extras/04682f10314d0d394cb0f5ddc5a14d81.avif?t=1753381252\" width=519 height=591 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >.........and more folks to find, too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTE</strong> - The game has a couple of small artistic symbolic illusions to body parts, as well as a reference to \"P\". Very PG overall, but keep that in mind if it's not your thing.<strong> </strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is presented in the style of old 1st-person point & click adventure games, with an emphasis on moody atmosphere and surreal environments. Strange denizens pepper the vast halls of this cryptic building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957880/extras/ede73aba2dc0f4af181f9418115a9aab.avif?t=1753381252\" width=366 height=194 /></span>Learn the mysteries of the various rooms and complete a handful of puzzle minigames to reach the \"true end\". Or just have a relaxed time exploring and meeting folks, because most of the station is accessible from when you first enter the building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will one of these fine folk become your artistic muse!?!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957880/extras/04682f10314d0d394cb0f5ddc5a14d81.avif?t=1753381252\" width=519 height=591 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >.........and more folks to find, too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTE</strong> - The game has a couple of small artistic symbolic illusions to body parts, as well as a reference to \"P\". Very PG overall, but keep that in mind if it's not your thing.<strong> </strong></p>",
